				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>PH Chew holds a pivotal role as the Director of Group Avows, offering invaluable insights and guidance in both business and technical domains. He plays a key part in shaping the direction and growth of Avows, demonstrating a strong commitment to the company&#8217;s development. <br /><br />Additionally, Mr. Chew serves as the Executive Director of a Software Company specializing in Islamic Core Banking and Treasury Management System development, sales, and implementation. The synergistic relationship between these two organizations bolsters their collective success. <br /><br />With a career that commenced in Financial Services in 1983, PH Chew has garnered extensive experience. Before joining Avows, he held the position of Technical Director and occupied senior roles within various prominent local national corporations in Malaysia. Over more than 38 years in the IT industry, Mr. Chew has played a crucial role in designing, developing, and implementing software systems across diverse sectors, including banking, hospital management, and human resource management. <br /><br />Mr. Chew&#8217;s academic qualifications include a Bachelor of Science (Honours) with a major in Computer Science from the United Kingdom, underscoring his solid educational foundation in the field. His multifaceted career, technical expertise, and dedication position him as an essential contributor to the growth and success of the Avows Group.</p>								</div>
