				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>In 2008, Ashok K. Ramavath embarked on a pioneering journey by founding Avows Technologies, driven by his visionary entrepreneurship. As the Group CEO, Ashok brings with him a wealth of knowledge and experience in technology and business consulting, spanning an impressive 20 years. His passion for nurturing the next generation of leadership has been a guiding force in developing strong and innovative technology teams at Avows, dedicated to meeting the complex and growing demands of clients in Southeast Asia. <br><br>Ashok&#8217;s remarkable strengths in achieving exceptional results in service delivery and financial performance have enabled Avows to assemble large and proficient teams of over 100 professionals. He is a member of the managing committee of CIIM (Consortium of Indian Industries in Malaysia) and firmly believes in Corporate Social Responsibility. Ashok&#8217;s proactive engagement with industry leaders has led to the creation of high-value solutions and service offerings in the IT &amp; ITES space from Avows, aligning with the organization&#8217;s core values and vision. <br><br>Under Ashok&#8217;s leadership, Avows Technologies has expanded its footprint, with its headquarters situated in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia, and additional offices and development centers in Singapore, Indonesia, India, the USA, and the UAE. Ashok&#8217;s outstanding contributions to the field of human resources were recognized during the Asia&#8217;s Best Employer Brand awards in 2010, and he was further acclaimed as &#8220;CEO of the Year 2013.&#8221; His unwavering commitment to innovation and social responsibility continues to drive Avows&#8217; success and growth.</p>								</div>
