									<p>Rakesh K Mudavath has been acting as President Director of PT Avows Technologies since November 2019. Under Rakesh’s visionary leadership, PT Avows Technologies has experienced a renaissance marked by exponential growth and consolidation of its position as the preferred choice of IT Technology partner for firms across Jakarta. With more than twelve years of experience in the IT sector, with a decade in the ASEAN market, Rakesh is a passionate leader who bridges the gap between business and technology.</p>
